For comparison, we also configure a simpler variant, {\bf CUP{{2311.01314_FO0020||FO}}}, which uses genre tags from the user's training items as the user text. 
To observe the effect of item metadata, we further restrict this variant to use only the item title and genre as item text, denoted as CUP{{2311.01314_FO0021||FO}}.